# 4. Tripartite Root Constraints

# 00_spirit: Always commit the Anchor and the Logic.
!00_spirit/**

# 00_spirit exceptions: Ignore massive scripture artifacts
00_spirit/scripture/KJV/**/*.txt
00_spirit/scripture/WEB/**/*.txt
