00_spirit/scripture/indices/**/*.bin
00_spirit/scripture/indices/**/*.trit

# 01_mind: Always commit the Witness and the Identity.
!01_mind/**

# 02_body: Commit the Core and Tools, but ignore the large-scale test artifacts.
02_body/test_mind/
02_body/tov/**/*.pdf
02_body/tov/**/*.png

# 5. Dependency Locks (The Structural Connectors)
